          <text><![CDATA[<p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to repeal the prohibition against churches and other tax-exempt organizations participating in political campaigns or supporting or opposing candidates for public office. Provides that this repeal shall not invalidate or limit any provision of the Federal Election Campaign Act of 1971.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-01-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
